nvy but in two cases: a man whom Allah has given wealth and he spends it rightly, and a man whom Allah has given wisdom and he judges and teaches with it.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14890,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/do-not-neglect-suhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":35817,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Suhoor: Do not neglect blessed pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Harith reported: A man among the companions entered upon the Prophet while he was eating the pre-fasting meal. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, it is a blessing that Allah has given you, so do not abandon it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2162 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25603,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/14\/allah-blesses-as-long-as-give\/","url_meta":{"origin":35817,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Blessings: Allah blesses them as long as they give","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has people for whom He has assigned blessings to benefit His servants. He consolidates their blessings as long as they offer them to others. If they refuse to give them, He takes them away\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35302,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/24\/love-allah-messenger-ahl-bayt\/","url_meta":{"origin":35817,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Mahabbah: Love Allah, His Messenger, and Ahl al-Bayt","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 24, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLove Allah for the blessings by which He nourishes you, love me for the love of Allah, and love the people of my house for the love of me.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3789 Grade: Hasan (fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11819,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/allah-loves-see-blessings\/","url_meta":{"origin":35817,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Bounties: Allah loves to see His blessings on His servants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Zuhayr ibn Abi 'Alqamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty loves to see the traces of blessings on his servant. He does not love one who wallows in misery and pessimism.\" Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 5167 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u064f\u0647\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u